  "description": "Autistic comedian Adam Schwartz (Aspergers a Tale of A social Misfit) and ADHD comedian Carole Cunningham (Yuk Yuks and the Debaters) bring together the funniest, most talented neurodivergent guest performers Edmonton Fringe has to offer in an hour so brilliantly awkward and hilarious, you'll be wondering did they just say that?",
